name: Youjin Lee
text: great pizza! I ordered online and carried out pizzas for my daughter's birthday. They gave me plates, napkins, and extra dipping sauces. I had great experience with them!

name: Irene Brown
text: Just like every other Papa John's. The taste is all right. Nothing special but not disgusting either. They have good take out specials and that's why we go there. Order online for the best deals.

name: Edith Layug
text: We been here just this day for about 40 minutes ago we order the hawain  pizza for to go. If i can give a 0 star for the guy in the register. He is so very rude and he never know how to smile. And the pizza that we ordered it does have much pineapple. This is the first time that i’ve met this kind of rude guy

name: Adam Lindgren
text: Delivery: minimum 40-50 minute wait, which is excessive for a delivery pizza joint. Their delivery estimate are often 15-30 minutes off, and the pizza arrives lukewarm. They charge delivery cost, unlike other pizza joints, and expect a …More

name: Tim Maland
text: I loved having this location downtown. Too bad it's closed now.

name: Emma Morris
text: Good quality, great prices. Much better than Pizza Hut! This location is clean, friendly, and very quick.

name: Kira Budinger
text: Who the hell stops delivering at 9 pm? All the other locations deliver until 11. Wasted my time. Worst papa johns location ever.

name: Andy B
text: Always had good service and great pizza. 10-15 minute wait max for pick up. Definitely one of my favorite pizza places.

name: Skyler Gonsalves
text: This place has amazing deals! And with the right kinds of toppings is actually one of the healthier pizzas I've had. Bravo Papa John

name: Jodi Church
text: I always oder online because I like to get the discounts and points and whether I pick up or have it delivered, it seems to take only about 15 minutes. The pizza is always good and hot. The service is always very friendly.

name: charles patnoe
text: they have a manager named john, he makes some awesome pizza's i have gone in there and it really seems like the place has improved recently not sure if it was him or not but when i wonder if i want a pizza i go there. i moved farther away and still drive the 15 min to pic up my pizza.

name: Josh Kieffer
text: I was looking to place an order on Monday, April 25th, with the Bellevue Papa Johns location, but when I called at 9:45am and 10:15am there was no answer and eventually went to a dial tone. As I am a big fan of the quality, variety, and …More

name: Farida M
text: Papa John's is the best pizza I ever ate.
